{"id":232817961,"title":"這種房型可以怎麼裝潢","content":"https://i.imgur.com/oTMbiC3.jpg\n房型是2+1狹長型房型\n一主臥一次臥\n客廳可以在隔間多一個房間\n或者像樣品屋一樣\n客廳後面可以用個電腦桌旁邊有個臥榻\n直接變一個大客廳\n客廳及主臥外面各有一個陽台\n廚房也是狹長型的\n\n目前我們是兩個人住\n次臥打算改建成更衣室\n主臥不要放衣櫥\n\n浴室及廚房的部分買房時已經有了\n剩下的部分都還沒弄\n希望大家可以給我些建議\n尤其是客廳跟電腦房跟廚房的部分\n怎麼裝潢比較好\n\n預算大概100萬左右\n權狀坪數40坪左右\n扣公設30多坪\n\n有載pinterest欣賞各種裝潢\n希望有多一些收納空間\n也想聽看看大家的建議","excerpt":"房型是2+1狹長型房型，一主臥一次臥，客廳可以在隔間多一個房間，或者像樣品屋一樣，客廳後面可以用個電腦桌旁邊有個臥榻，直接變一個大客廳，客廳及主臥外面各有一個陽台，廚房也是狹長型的，目前我們是兩個人住","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"5b964198-2e59-419d-b44c-0276d0fea7e8","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-03T10:46:48.470Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-03T10:47:18.676Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["裝潢","房型","居家佈置","改造","WhatsInMyRoom"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"居家生活","forumAlias":"house","school":"queen","department":"if_you__","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/oTMbiC3.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f59dd2b2-eaa3-4c9e-b8a3-8c92c6008844","url":"https://i.imgur.com/oTMbiC3l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/oTMbiC3l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/oTMbiC3l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-03T10:46:48.470Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-03T10:47:18.676Z"},{"id":"f59dd2b2-eaa3-4c9e-b8a3-8c92c6008844","url":"https://i.imgur.com/oTMbiC3.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/oTMbiC3","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/oTMbiC3l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-03T10:46:48.470Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-03T10:47:18.676Z"}],"postAvatar":""}